&kp LC(DOUBLE_QUOTES)  &kp LS(AMPS)   &kp STAR  &kp EXCL  &kp LS(LT)  &kp LS(GT)    &kp FSLH       &kp LBKT      &kp RBKT        &kp LS(QUESTION)  &kp BSLH      &kp PIPE
                                                &trans    &kp SPACE   &tog 2        &mo 3          &kp SPACE     &kp LEFT_SHIFT
            >;
